          }
        ],
        "headline": "What makes Columbia the ‘activist Ivy’?",
        "dek": "A year after Columbia’s “Gaza Solidarity Encampment” swept the nation, student activists and professors reflect on the University’s history of activism.",
        "date": "May 6, 2025",
        "byline": "By <a href=\"https://www.columbiaspectator.com/contributors/isha-banerjee/\">Isha Banerjee</a> and <a href=\"https://www.columbiaspectator.com/contributors/emily-pickering/\">Emily Pickering</a>",
